review_text: Nice little neighbourhood park with a nice green space and little woods next to it. It's still early in the season (May), but a little maintenance would be helpful. There was a swing missing and the water fountain was still inoperable. But a still a great park for neighbourhood kids.
The most quiet park in the area, two other parks I went to were too loud and full of screaming children
